  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study investigates the effect of the Mothers Touch program on the psychological
      well-being of new mothers following 5 weeks of child birth. Mothers Touch Program is designed
      based on traditional Indian post-partum care given by trained carer in the family.

      Study was designed as cohort, including a randomised controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
